You invoked \`triple-plan\`. Execute the following protocol exactly.

## Roles
- **Planners (parallel):** claude-opus-4.7-xhigh, claude-opus-4.6-1m, gpt-5.5
- **Judge (synthesizes the plans into the final canonical plan):** claude-opus-4.6-1m
- **Expected premium calls:** 4 happy path (3 planners + 1 judge); 8 worst case (with retries).

> **Note on judge default:** triple-plan's judge defaults to a 1M-context model variant because three planner outputs can easily exceed the ~200k context of \`-xhigh\`. Pass \`judge: "claude-opus-4.7-xhigh"\` if you want the deeper-reasoning variant and your plans are small enough to fit.

